short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhance your learning with BuildUp’s Pathfinder AI Agent! It offers personalized challenges for hands-on skill development.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhance your learning journey with AI-driven problem-solving! BuildUp’s Pathfinder AI Agent. Extension provides personalized, real-world challenges for students, promoting hands-on skill development through problem-based learning. 

Once user enroll in the official courses at BuildUp's website, the extension delivers custom challenges tailored to the user's learning goals and preferences. As students navigate websites or work on projects, Pathfinder Agent follows their progress, offering real-time guidance, tips, and support to tackle practical issues effectively. This hands-on tool ensures focused, practical learning experiences while fostering critical thinking and creativity.

Version 1.3 - Minor bugs fixed.
